==English==
===Etymology===
Named after the [[swindler]] Carlo (''Charles'') Ponzi.
===Noun===
'''Ponzi scam''' (Plural '''Ponzi scams''')
# A [[fraudulant]] [[scheme]] where earlier [[investors]] are paid with the money taken from new investors, giving the [[impression]] that the scheme is a [[viable]] [[investment]].

